1.title: Pilot
1.plot: Another year of school begins for the privileged that matriculate at Westfield Prep.

2.title: Like a Lion in the Savannah
2.plot: Mallorie and Drew try to contact the spirits of his deceased parents.

3.title: Oh, She Goes to Stockdale..
3.plot: Drew meets Rick. A romantic connection between Sean and Mallorie comes to light.

4.title: Trainwreck! It's Your Favorite!
4.plot: Rick is tormented by his actions. Mallorie and Sean try to deal with Drew's memory issues.

5.title: Pictures of People I Don't Recognize
5.plot: Mallorie and Sean push Drew to remember his former life.

6.title: Teddy Gram for Mr. Castle
6.plot: Sean and Mallorie heat things up. Rick unintentionally makes his presence known to Drew.

7.title: Back to School, Again
7.plot: Drew's first day back at Westfield is quite memorable.

8.title: Confrontation
8.plot: Mallorie realizes she is jealous when she sees Sean flirting with someone else. Drew, starting to have flashbacks from his attack, begins seeing a therapist.

9.title: Revenge
9.plot: There's nothing worse than uncertainty. It can destroy the soul slowly.

10.title: A Boy Named Oliver
10.plot: Drew begins to push boundaries. Mallorie and Sean might be over.

11.title: Prom
11.plot: Everything has been leading up to this night.

12.title: A New Gang
12.plot: Drew has a change of heart. Sean and Mallorie fight to be together.
